You are trapped in the CAVEZ of PHEAR. You must make it out of 
all the caves alive. To advance to the next cave collect all 
diamonds.

Diamond - * - 10 points
Money - $ - 100 points
Extra life every 1000 points.

Movement - Arrow keys, numpad, or WSAD

Toggle mute - M
Show position - F
Restart level - R
Save - O
Load - L
Pause - P

Bombs - %
		B to place 
		T to detonate

Monsters - M
		Rocks and bombs are effective against them,
		but they're lethal if they catch up.

Rocks - O
		Squishing hazard.

Send comments, questions, requests, bugs, and other feedback to
tom@x86.no or steve@asksteved.com.
